bilingual.source: Collective wisdom is stronger than individual wisdom.
bilingual.target: 集体的智慧比个人的智慧更强大。

bilingual.source: Solving this problem requires our collective brainpower.
bilingual.target: 解决这个问题需要我们集体的脑力。

bilingual.source: The team's failure led to a collective disillusionment among the fans.
bilingual.target: 团队的失败导致了粉丝们集体的失望。

bilingual.source: The responsibility is collective because this is the most loved monument in the country.
bilingual.target: 这个责任是集体的，因为这是该国最受人喜爱的纪念碑。
影响到集体的因缘(因果报应).

bilingual.source: But to beat emeny we must use collective force.
bilingual.target: 但要打败敌人，我们要用集体的力量。

bilingual.source: Chorus is a collective vocality performing art.
bilingual.target: 合唱是集体的声乐表演艺术。

bilingual.source: Is to maximize the general welfare, or the collective happiness,
bilingual.target: 就是将公共福利，或集体的幸福最大化，

bilingual.source: There is no such thing as a collective conscience, collective kindness, collective gentleness, collective freedom.
bilingual.target: 没有所谓集体的良心，集体善心，集体亲切，集体自由。

bilingual.source: And what is true of individuals is also true for collective entities, collective nouns like states and cities.
bilingual.target: 适用于个人的真理,也同样适用于集体的实体，集体的名词，像是城与邦。

yingyinNormal.en: I talked about our collective strength, black and white, coming together during times of crisis.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我提到了我们集体的力量，无论是黑人还是白人，在危机时刻走到一起。

yingyinNormal.en: Despite the risks of this collective existence, many species use the reef as a nursery.
yingyinNormal.zh: 尽管这种集体生活存在风险，很多物种还是将珊瑚礁作为了栖息地。

yingyinNormal.en: At 12:01 Friday morning, the NBA locked out its players after failing to reach a new collective bargaining agreement.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在周五早上12点01分，NBA停摆了。所有的球员因为劳资双方无法在新一轮的集体谈判上达成一致。

yingyinNormal.en: It is the moment when our nation's resilience, when our collective strength, the moment when all of that is tested the most.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是检验我国坚韧的时刻，检验人民团结的时刻，最能检验一切的时刻。

yingyinNormal.en: He's putting his needs ahead of the collective good. Where he comes from, that's punishable by death. I come from Sacramento.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他把自己的利益置于集体利益之前，在这位老兄的家乡，那可是死罪。我是萨克拉门托人。

yingyinNormal.en: The collective bargaining process has completely broken down. We're all in this together. And if these players don't give them what they want, they're not going to play.
yingyinNormal.zh: 劳资双方的工资谈判过程已经完全破裂，我们都身处其中，如果这些球员不给他们想要的，他们是不会开工的

yingyinNormal.en: And even if someone slipped a chill pill into their collective drink, you would still be legally unable to work for the next two years. That's for any studio, any network. Television or film.
yingyinNormal.zh: 即使有人往他们公共饮用水里放了镇静药，在法律约束下，你未来两年都无法工作。无论是在哪家工作室、电视台、电视剧或是电影。

yingyinNormal.en: In the past, I've reached out to each of you individually, but I believe my present situation requires the collective wisdom of the group, which as you can see from your commemorative T-shirts I have dubbed Sheldon Cooper's Council of Ladies.
yingyinNormal.zh: 过去呢，我曾与在座各位有过单独请益的时刻，但这次我觉得这次的情况需要你们一起共同集思广益，想必你们从纪念T恤上也能看得出，我标注上了“谢尔顿·库伯姐妹顾问团”。

数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: We need progressive policies that shape <highlight>collective</highlight> action (and rein in polluting businesses), alongside engaged citizens pushing for change.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们需要形成集体行动（并控制污染企业）的进步政策，以及推动变革的积极公民。

examination_example.sentence: There's no change to <highlight>collective</highlight> bargaining at the USPS, a major omission considering that personnel accounts for 80 percent of the agency's costs.
examination_example.sentence_trans: USPS的集体谈判没有改变，考虑到人事成本占机构成本的80%，这是一个重大遗漏。

examination_example.sentence: For a generation, the <highlight>collective</highlight> doctrine has been that the sorting mechanism of society should be profit.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一代人以来，集体主义一直认为社会的分类机制应该是利润。
